reviewText: This video has some of the best indy wrestling that NorCal has to offer.  Great wrestling action from start to finish, awesome color commentary from Lars Frederiksen of Rancid & the one and only Kevin Gill of JCW plus it's a tribute to the memory of DJ Rizz!!!  You can't go wrong with this one.
Everyone should check this out to see what NorCal wrestling has to offer and to support the memory of a guy who was loved and respected my a huge family of not only wrestlers but fans alike.
There's something great about NorCal wrestling that is caught here on video. If you want to watch some great matches I highly recommend this dvd!
Really interesting show. I highly recommend it! Great tribute a person that was and still is very important to many people. Jason Lee Smith/"DJ Rizz"!
If you love the CA indie wrestling scene you'll love this. Hell and if you don't might as well get into it
This is a great dvd.  Showcases some of the best in the CA indie wrestling scene.  Support the future of pro wrestling and purchase this.  You won't be disappointed.
this dvd was awsome good wrestling good story and good people Dj Rizz is gone but never forgotten love u cuzzy
This was a good wrestling tournament to honor a very gifted wrestler, DJ Rizz! Wish I could have been there live!
This is an Awesome wrestling dvd. don't miss out on it! Support Indy Wrestling! this would make a great gift for any wrestling fan!
